  m_text: "This screen shows the total invested resources by the players in all the
    methods. \nTake some time and discuss these investments, if everyone is satisfied
    then the players should move ahead with methods development. \r\n\nDiscuss amongst
    all the colleagues and make a collective decision. The Master can choose the
    preferred option in the Game UI\r\n\nREMEMBER: Once you move forward to methods
    development, you can\u2019t invest resources in this round again, it will only
    be in the next round\r\n"
