  m_text: "Hello! It seems like you have used all the time you had to go through
    the \ndifferent phases of the project. Hopefully, you were able to go through
    the various methods, saw how they could be used in development of a smart grill
    \nand also how different roles were crucial to different methods.\_\_\n\nAre
    you ready to see how you did in this game? The next page would take your game
    end report card and show how well you did.\_\_\n\nAll the Best!"
