  m_text: "Congratulations! You completed all the phases of this project. You went
    through the various methods, saw how they could be used in development of a smart
    grill. You saw how different roles were crucial to different methods.\_\_\n\nAre
    you ready to see how you did in this game? The next page would take your game
    end report card and show how well you did.\_\_\n\nAll the Best!"
